 Spice Girls的“ Spice Up Your Life”现在受到广播电台的审查https://www.nme.com/news/music/spice/spice-girls-spice-up-your-your-life-is-now-censored-censored-radio-station--3849333?utm_source = rss间Liberty DunworthWed, 26 Mar 2025 10:31:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3849333 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="香料女孩在1997年表演。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于有争议的歌词，正在播放一个受过审查的版本</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spice-girls-spice-up-your-life-is-now-censored-by-radio-stations-3849333">现在，广播电台</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上审查了Spice Girls的“ Spice up Your Life”。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="香料女孩在1997年表演。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/spice-girls@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spice-girls">Spice Girls</a>的热门歌曲“ Spice Up您的生活”现在受到广播电台的审查。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/opinion/spice-girls-wannabe-at-25-2988871">25岁的香料女孩的“想念”：从那以后我们从标志性的女孩团体中学到了什么</a></strong></li></ul><p>该小组的经典曲目于1997年首次分享，并成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mel-b">Mel B</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/melanie-c">Melanie C</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emma-bunton">Emma Bunton</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geri-halliwell">Geri Halliwell</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/victoria-beckham">Victoria Beckham</a>的最知名曲目之一。发布后，它在图表的前20个星期中停留了六个星期，然后在12个前40名中保持了12个。</p><p>但是，这首歌中有争议的线条导致该曲目现在受到众多广播电台的审查。</p><p>最初的歌词上写着：“<em>我和您的timbuktu。颜色的黄色男人</em>”，尽管包括BBC Radio 2在内的广播电台现在正在播放The Hit的修订版，其中已删除了“黄色”一词。</p><p>关于歌词的争议也可以追溯到2019年，当时有报道称该小组正在考虑为当年的团圆巡回演出代替“黄色”一词。这个决定后来被抛弃了，他们用原始歌词播放了这首歌。</p><p> <em><a href="https://metro.co.uk/2025/03/26/iconic-spice-girls-song-censored-bbc-radio-2-stations-controversial-lyric-22793601/?ito=newsnow-feed" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Metro</a></em>还强调，审查版的热门歌曲是在2023年Doctor Who剧集中播放的，当时角色在歌词上讲话。</p><p> BBC Radio 2的一位代表与<a href="https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/34050307/bbc-censor-spice-girls-spice-up-your-life/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Sun</em></a>分享了一份声明，称该编辑不是由他们进行的，而是由众多电台播放的修正版本。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="香料女孩 - 增添您的生活（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9wfpXI5PKlw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>至于香料女孩，有关团体团聚的谣言已经流传了多年，去年四月，当成员们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-beckham-shares-video-of-private-spice-girls-reunion-for-victorias-50th-birthday-celebra